Using PHPMailer with Composer

Download and install composer
https://getcomposer.org/
Create Projects: Create your PHP projects (project1, project2, etc.) in separate directories as usual.

Run Composer Once: For each project, navigate to the project directory (cd path/to/project1, cd path/to/project2, etc.) and run composer require phpmailer/phpmailer once in each project directory.
install 7-zip and git
```
composer require phpmailer/phpmailer
```
```
choco install unzip
```
